      <title>华尔街SPAC热潮的产物Airspan寻求快速破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/airspan-child-of-wall-street-spac-craze-seeks-quick-bankruptcy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Airspan Networks Holdings Inc.获得法院批准，试图以比正常更快的速度削减破产债务，使其在成为华尔街SPAC繁荣中最新的财务崩溃之后迅速扭转局面。]]></description>
