    <item>
      <title>由于现金紧缩，科技投资公司破坏性地让三分之二的员工休假</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/disruptive-furloughed-two-thirds-of-employees-amid-cash-crunch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，专注于技术的投资公司 Disruptive 已让约三分之二的员工暂时休假，以应对因收费方式造成的现金短缺问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/disruptive-furloughed-two-thirds-of-employees-amid-cash-crunch</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 16:06:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊取消美国杂货店的无收银系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/amazon-pulls-plug-on-cashierless-system-in-us-grocery-stores</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司(Amazon.com Inc.)正在从杂货店中取消其无收银员Just Walk Out技术，这是对旨在让购物者免排队的雄心勃勃的系统的撤退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/amazon-pulls-plug-on-cashierless-system-in-us-grocery-stores</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 15:46:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通交易和复活节电话是智利公司 WOM 破产前的最后一步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/jpmorgan-deal-easter-call-were-last-steps-before-wom-bankruptcy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的智利电信运营商 WOM 在复活节周日上午 7 点的一次会议上决定了自己的命运，这场会议结束了债权人数月的焦虑和最后一刻的融资谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/jpmorgan-deal-easter-call-were-last-steps-before-wom-bankruptcy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 15:31:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Autodesk 正在探索自己的会计实践，股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/autodesk-launches-internal-probe-into-accounting-practices-stock-declines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧特克公司(Autodesk Inc.)在披露对其自身会计实践的内部调查并推迟发布年度财务报告后，股价创下近一个月以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/autodesk-launches-internal-probe-into-accounting-practices-stock-declines</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 14:24:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
